verbose_text: Alterations of IgLON gene expression levels in the frontal cortex and hippocampus of wild-type and mutant mice were analyzed by one-way ANOVA in parallel in two mutant subgroups : Group I included Wt (wild-type), Lsamp -/-, Lsamp -/- / Ntm -/-, and Group II included Wt, Ntm -/-, Lsamp -/- / Ntm -/- at significance level of alpha = 0.05.
